				<wikidot:authorName>Inkary</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>5108517</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I like this scp so much because it's sort of comedic relief character minus comedic part. So, calm relief object? Nevermind.</p> <p>It's sorta mysterious and unexplained like some dangerous keters, but it's the opposite of that. It's a change of pace after reading about triple digits of casualities caused by a breach, making you really feel how dangerous those (other) scps are. And on the other hand, this scp makes you think woah, not every scp is spooky scary many people died and will die, while it's nature and purpose of creation remains a mystery.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
